OL,3,C'My car fell apart on the motorway" `
OL,4,CWarning to buyers of used vehicles
OL,6,FA woman has issued a warning to buyers
OL,7,Fof used vehicles after a car she
OL,8,Fbought "fell apart" on the motorway.
OL,10,FDriving along the M3 motorway in
OL,11,FMarch, Tracy Barber had a terrifying
OL,12,Fexperience.
OL,14,F"My car fell apart on me," she told
OL,15,FITV Wales.
OL,17,F"I ended up with no steering, no
OL,18,Fbrakes at 70mph, which nearly killed
OL,19,Fme.
