OL,3,C'My car fell apart on the motorway" `
OL,4,CWarning to buyers of used vehicles
OL,6,F"The wheel sheared off, the brake
OL,7,Fcalipers and the brakes ended up
OL,8,Fbehind my car, and there was fluid
OL,9,Finside of it."
OL,11,FShe had bought the 2015 plate Hyundai
OL,12,Fi40 only a month before.
OL,14,FTracy, who lives in the West Country,
OL,15,Fbrowsed the website Car Finance 247, a
OL,16,Fsite which allowed her to search for
OL,17,Fcars and finance providers.
OL,19,FShe chose a vehicle from Tredegar-
OL,20,Fbased dealership Desirable Motors.
