OL,3,C'My car fell apart on the motorway" `
OL,4,CWarning to buyers of used vehicles
OL,6,FThe car was bought through a finance
OL,7,Fagreement with the lender Moneybarn.
OL,9,FAfter the incident, she complained to
OL,10,FCar Finance 247, Moneybarn and
OL,11,FDesirable Motors.
OL,13,FShe then took her case to the
OL,14,FFinancial Ombudsman Service.
OL,16,FIt accepted the car had already done
OL,17,F116,000 miles, and a further 1,500 in
OL,18,Fher ownership.
