OL,4,CWarning to buyers of used vehicles
OL,6,FLauren Nation, from Citizens Advice
OL,7,FCaerphilly Blaenau Gwent, urges people
OL,8,Fto check the terms and conditions of
OL,9,Fany purchase.
OL,11,FShe said: "Cars are very mechanical,
OL,12,Fso things just do go wrong with them,
OL,13,Fbut this is why we do stress that if
OL,14,Fyou're buying online you do things
OL,15,Flike check the reviews, get down there
OL,16,Fto see the vehicle.
OL,18,F"When buying at a distance, you do get
OL,19,Fa 14-day cooling off period, so read
OL,20,Fup on that as well.
