OL,4,CWarning to buyers of used vehicles
OL,6,F"If you're using a car marketplace,
OL,7,Fit's always important to check your
OL,8,Fterms and conditions, so that you
OL,9,Funderstand first and foremost who your
OL,10,Frights are going to be against,
OL,11,Fbecause you could be buying through
OL,12,Fthem, but you may have rights with the
OL,13,Fgarage itself, or may have rights with
OL,14,Fthe finance company if you're going
OL,15,Fthrough the finance company as well".
OL,17,FThe charity says problems with used
OL,18,Fvehicles are its most common
OL,19,Fcomplaints.
